Available Tools: get_instance_status | list_instances | get_instance_metrics
Call Schema: { "func_call": "string", "instance_id": "string", "region": "string", "filter": "string" }
Response Schema: { "instances": [{ "id": "string", "type": "string", "state": "string", "ip": "string" }] }
---
Question: What are the disk I/O and CPU stats for instance i-1f2e3d4c5b6a in us-west-1?
Call: { "func_call": "get_instance_metrics", "instance_id": "i-1f2e3d4c5b6a", "region": "us-west-1", "filter": "disk,cpu" }
Response: { "instances": [{ "id": "i-1f2e3d4c5b6a", "type": "m5.2xlarge", "state": "running", "ip": "172.31.55.23" }] }

Question: Show me memory pressure and network errors for app-server-dev-02 in eu-west-3.
Call: { "func_call": "get_instance_metrics", "instance_id": "app-server-dev-02", "region": "eu-west-3", "filter": "memory,network" }
Response: { "instances": [{ "id": "app-server-dev-02", "type": "t3.large", "state": "running", "ip": "10.0.15.99" }] }

